This application demonstrates use of OAuth2 protocol to login to Github using a third party app such as this one. 

Make sure before logging in using this application, to logout of github user which will be used as demo.

To allow a third party application to access a github account, we need to create an Auth app in Github, link reference
provided below

clientId and clientSecret in application.properties need to be updated as per the Github Auth App

Reference:

https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CWiwpvpCrro&ab_channel=JavaBrains

https://docs.github.com/en/developers/apps/creating-an-oauth-app

https://www.baeldung.com/spring-security-oauth2-enable-resource-server-vs-enable-oauth2-sso